@gdm85 Unfortunately, `fuser-overlayfs` does not solve the problem. If you recheck this thread carefully, you will notice that I documented many attempts with it (e.g. in the [OP](https://github.com/containers/buildah/issues/1818#issue-484699046) where I copy it from my local system inside the container).

> I could not build fuse-overlays because it requires fuse3 which is not available on the current Ubuntu LTS (bionic)

`fuse3` is not required: see updated instructions for the build [here](https://github.com/containers/fuse-overlayfs#static-build). I too use Ubuntu 18.04, and perform the build with those steps.
